aw enforcement officers; supervisory staff at community corrections agencies, probation officers, parole officers, and correctional officers, among others. Learn more about Criminal Justice at UNT.  Four-Year Plan 2016-2017  Planning Sheet 2016-2017  Program Requirements 2016-2017  UNT Catalog 2016-2017  Now you can earn your degree on campus at UNT in Denton, at UNT\u2019s New College in Frisco or 100% online. Apply now.For more information, contact the Academic Advising Office. Academic advisors for Criminal Justice majors are Anthony Vasquez (last names A-K) and Rachel Rachel (last names L-Z). Our graduate adviser is Dr. Adam Trahan.                       Visit Us    Chilton Hall 265 [map]        Mail Us Criminal Justice   1155 Union Circle #305130   Denton,       TX 76203-5017      Contact Us  Phone: (940) 565-2562 Fax: (940) 565-2548 Email: D'Ann.Hammett@unt.edu            Last updated April 12, 2017   Disclaimer         |         AA/EOE/ADA         |         Privacy          |          Electronic Accessibility         |         State of Texas Online         |         Emergency Preparedness         |         THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information         |         UNT Compliance Hotline         |         Governors Committee on People with Disabilities         |         Texas Veterans Portal         |         UNT Home                         
